1 B. Nothing in this section shall be construed to alter or
2 revoke the status of any municipality, corporation, association,
3 partnership, nonprofit organization, or other legal entity duly
4 recognized under the laws of this state prior to November 1, 2026.
5 SECTION 2. This act shall become effective November 1, 2026.
6 COMMITTEE REPORT BY: COMMITTEE ON TECHNOLOGY AND TELECOMMUNICATIONS
